about.summary: Concurrent logging handler (drop-in replacement for RotatingFileHandler) Python 2.6+

name: concurrentloghandler
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ConcurrentLogHandler" %}
{% set version = "0.9.1" %}
{% set sha256sum = "8225a590fd4194c413fa26675bde5f6b80ad79e4182d5876ba3e264f77755918" %}

package:
  name: {{ name.lower() }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256sum }}

build:
  number: 1000
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python
    - pywin32  # [win]

test:
  imports:
    - cloghandler

about:
  home: https://launchpad.net/python-concurrent-log-handler
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE'
  summary: Concurrent logging handler (drop-in replacement for RotatingFileHandler) Python 2.6+

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mariusvniekerk
